    "creativeSuggestion": "视频素材 #CR58392 表现最佳，建议增加变体预算；图片素材 CPI 偏高可暂停观察。"
  },
  "api": {
    "url": "POST /api/v1/datacenter/analysis/ad-performance/campaign-detail/ad-detail/overview",
    "method": "POST",
    "priority": "P0",
    "requestBody": "adId, campaignId",
    "responseBody": "AdDetailData"
  },
  "apiSuggestion": {
    "notes": [
      "数值字段与 types.ts 严格一致；展示格式化由前端负责。",
      "若网关统一包裹，业务体置于 data。"
    ]
  }
}
